data.title: VonZipper : Dan Brisse in the Feenom & Skylab
data.description:
Feenom: The Godfather of all goggles, the Feenom hands out a whole lotta steez to make them fall to their knees and repent if you please.

Skylab: Defy the laws of gravity and take a moon shot in the Skylab. The captain of the Milky Way, your game will orbit the outer limits in this spherical space shield.

data.title: VonZipper : Snow Team 2012
data.description: VonZipper is about lifestyle and personality. Our mission is to develop, design and deliver premium eyewear, goggles, soft goods and accessories to the alternative mindset through participation in the sideways subculture and a commitment to the individual. Everything we do is a reflection of relationships from employees and team riders, to our retailers and their customers. We bring smiles to faces and touch people with positive declarations of rebellion against the norm.

data.title: VonZipper : Ether Collection
data.description: The ether collection by VonZipper is a full frontal assault on frames being technical without losing design creativity and edge. Here's where the rubber hits the road. If you wanna rip, have lots of grip, with no slip, our RGNS system features rubber nose pads and temple tips. These lightweight frames with pop-n-lock hinges simplify the construction and make them more flexible and durable, so you can compete without looking or being beat. Burn your training bra and toss your jockstrap out the window.

data.title: VonZipper : Optical 2012
data.description: Lock and load your pocket protectors, pack up your scientific calculators, light up the bunsen burner... The Retina Revolutionaries at VonZipper are here to unite all inner nerds to fight for the right of sight. Mixing geek chic contemporary looks with renegade sheik forwardness, this collection has every angle on your protractor covered to get you through all the fine print in life! Whether you are an intellectual mastermind, a naughty librarian, or an IT tech searching for individuality, VonZipper optical is bringing the focus back to the eye chart.

data.title: VonZipper : Charity for Clarity
data.description:
Knowing that seeing is believing and we believe in seeing,Vonzipper will donate one optical frame for every optical frame we sell. With a simple purchase of a frame, a life is changed forever, and that's a real eye-opener.

Throughout the world, the cost of eyeglasses is far beyond the reach of the needy. In many developing nations the cost of a frame can be the equivalent to one year's salary. Without assistance, thousands of people go without the glasses that they need to read, work, attend school and do the everyday activities that we take for granted.

The Retina Revolutionaries from VonZipper are here to fight for the right of sight, as it is our mission to bring the vision! We feel that it is important to share our success and hope that you will share our focus. So join us in giving something back and become a Pupillary Missionary!

data.title: VonZipper : Weeman & Donavon Frankenreiter Shift Into Neutral
data.description: Truth be told, VZ has the hots for Mother Nature... So much in fact, we hug trees on a daily basis. It's with that embrace in mind; we're launching Shift Into Neutral -- a collection of sunglasses that are made from the environmentally friendly and sustainable materials.
